    <div class="body">
        <p>If you want to pass the '$source' parameter in __construct() by reference you need to add the '&amp;' operator by
assigning the variable at line 42:</p>

<ul><li><p>old
$this-&gt;_source = $source;</p></li>
<li><p>new
$this-&gt;_source = &amp; $source;</p></li>
</ul><p>Best regards
wego</p>

